Getting down to business

ILP is a leading U.S. manufacturer of LED Commercial, Industrial, and Outdoor lighting fixtures providing quality solutions designed to meet the ever-expanding market needs.


Our Capability

Wide Product Breadth

Over 500+ products, and growing, provide quality solutions for the Commercial, Industrial, and Outdoor market segments.

Speed To Market

Local manufacturing capabilities with a flexible production schedule and an onsite engineering team gives us the power to design and deliver products to the market faster than anyone.

Technical Sales Staff

Highly educated and trained sales staff with in-house applications engineer, able to provide layout designs within hours of new requests, will guide you through every lighting project ensuring you have a product that maximizes energy savings while still meeting your required light levels.

Responsive Customer Service Team

Dedicated team located on the East & West coast ensures there is always someone there to assist you with any questions regarding your order.
